This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with object detection and segmentation. Additionally, the paper proposes a mechanism to mimic the process of priming in neural networks, which falls under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses the effects of top-down signaling in the visual system, which is related to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of post-processing techniques, which is relevant to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) category.
